.DS_Store

# Heavy intermediates that the Dockerfile re-creates from scratch — never
# worth shipping into the build context. We deliberately do NOT exclude
# `web/build`: with `--build-arg SKIP_WEB_BUILD=true` you can pre-build the
# SPA on the host (handy when Docker Desktop's engine RAM is tight) and the
# Dockerfile picks up the artifacts straight from the context. A normal
# build re-generates `web/build` inside the bun stage anyway.
web/node_modules
web/.svelte-kit
